$ Oracle: incremental backup
@ incremental backup

An incremental only copies → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/database/logical-structures/data-block[blocks] that have changed since the last
→ development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/backup-recovery/backup. This information is stored in a *block change tracking file* (which is only written
if *block change trackin* is enabled).



→ development/databases/Oracle/tools/RMAN/commands[RMAN command]: `backup incremental`
